==Useful Info==
'''Sun moths''' are insects native to the [[Spider's Nest]] and occasionally appear in the realm of [[Cerebov]]. They can swoop behind foes and pelt them with [[Pyre Arrow]].

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*To avoid being set on fire by Pyre Arrow, hide behind other enemies.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.31]], sun moths were [[holy]] insects that used [[Sticky Flame Range]] and [[Energy Bolt]], had a single-tile halo, and would apply [[Sticky Flame]] upon biting a target. They were not found in Cerebov's realm.
*Sun moths were added in [[0.28]].
